channel.title: Server ip
channel.description: i have previously made servers and never had this problem. this is a new computer i got and i decided to host a server. so my CMd is running saying that my server is running, but when i put the ip in from "www.no-ip.com DUC" that is set up on my computer, it says error connecting to server, so i decided to test the server to see if it was that. I typed in 127.0.0.1 and i connected fine, someone please help me with my ip. Maybe we can use Team veiwer? PLEASE HELp
